'''GNU Guix'''（{{IPAc-en|ɡ|iː|k|s}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gnu.org/software/guix/manual/guix.html#FOOT1|title=GNU Guix Reference Manual|website=www.gnu.org|access-date=2018-04-23|archive-date=2018-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223161934/https://www.gnu.org/software/guix/manual/guix.html#FOOT1|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是一个跨平台的包管理器，也是一个用于实例化和管理类Unix操作系统的工具。其基于[[Nix_包管理器|Nix]]包管理器与[[Guile_Scheme_API|Guile Scheme API]]，只提供[[自由软件|自由软件]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Functional_Package_Management_with_Guix |title=Functional Package Management with Guix |author=Ludovic Courtès |date=2013 |location=[[Madrid|Madrid]], [[Spain|Spain]] |publisher=European Lisp Symposium |accessdate=2021-01-27 |archive-date=2015-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205214923/https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Functional_Package_Management_with_Guix |dead-url=no }}</ref> GNU Guix是[[GNU_Guix_System|GNU Guix System]]GNU/Linux发行版的默认包管理器。<ref name="What to call Guix">{{cite mailing list |title=What to call Guix? |publisher=gnu-system-discuss |date=2015-01-15 |url=http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/gnu-system-discuss/2015-01/threads.html |access-date=2021-01-27 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807015108/https://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/gnu-system-discuss/2015-01/threads.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AAA">{{Cite web |url=https://www.gnu.org/software/guix/manual/en/html_node/Programming-Interface.html |title=Programming Interface (GNU Guix Reference Manual) |accessdate=2021-01-27 |archive-date=2019-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190602190920/https://www.gnu.org/software/guix/manual/en/html_node/Programming-Interface.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBK">{{Cite web |url=https://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTIzNjY |title=Guix: A New Package Manager & GNU Distribution - Phoronix |accessdate=2021-01-27 |archive-date=2015-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202160820/http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTIzNjY |dead-url=no }}</ref>

与传统的[[包管理器|包管理器]]不同，Guix（如Nix一样）采用了纯功能部署模式，软件被安装到通过[[密码散列函数|密码散列]]生成的唯一的目录中。每个软件的依赖都包含在哈希当中，解决了[[依赖地狱|依赖地狱]]的问题。<ref>Prins, P., Suresh, J. and Dolstra, E., [http://www.linux.com/feature/155922 "Nix fixes dependency hell on all Linux distributions,"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.linux.com/feature/155922 |date=20081226010942 }} [[linux.com|linux.com]], December 22, 2008</ref> 这种包管理方法更有可能产生更可靠、可复制和[[移植_(軟體)|可移植]]的包。<ref>Dolstra, E., de Jonge, M. and Visser, E. [https://nixos.org/~eelco/pubs/nspfssd-lisa2004-final.pdf "Nix: A Safe and Policy-Free System for Software Deployment."] {{Wayback|url=https://nixos.org/~eelco/pubs/nspfssd-lisa2004-final.pdf |date=20181002051604 }} In Damon, L. (Ed.), ''[http://www.usenix.org/events/lisa04/ 18th Large Installation System Administration Conference (LISA '04)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usenix.org/events/lisa04/ |date=20120111131513 }}'', pages 79–92, Atlanta, Georgia, USA. USENIX, November 2004.</ref><ref>Dolstra, E. [https://nixos.org/~eelco/pubs/phd-thesis.pdf ''The Purely Functional Software Deployment Model.''] {{Wayback|url=https://nixos.org/~eelco/pubs/phd-thesis.pdf |date=20190609111633 }} PhD thesis, Faculty of Science, Utrecht, The Netherlands. January 2006. {{ISBN|90-393-4130-3}}.</ref>

Guix 中的包使用一种专用的，名为Guile Scheme API的语言来进行定义。<ref name="x">{{Cite web|title=GNU's advanced distro and transactional package manager — GNU Guix|url=http://guix.gnu.org/|accessdate=2021-01-29|work=guix.gnu.org|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127091350/https://guix.gnu.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>依赖通过被称为“派生”的特殊值在这种语言中被跟踪，这些值将被Guix进程评估。Guix 会跟踪这些值，以便在没有其他软件包依赖它们时，可以被删除。以更大的存储需求为代价，Guix保证其所有操作是原子操作并可被回滚。<ref name="x" />

GNU Guix的开发与GNU Guix System交织在一起（直到Guix 1.0：Guix系统发行版[GuixSD]）。<ref name="What to call Guix"/>GNU Guix System是一个使用[[Hurd|Hurd]]内核和GNU Shepherd init系统的完整的GNU系统。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hurd 内核接棒：GNU Guix 将终止对 Linux 的支持|url=https://www.ithome.com/0/481/232.htm|accessdate=2021-02-03|author=|date=2020-04-05|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925070626/https://www.ithome.com/0/481/232.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AAA" /><ref name="BBK" />

